umn-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 20px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="vc_separator wpb_content_element vc_separator_align_center vc_sep_width_100 vc_sep_pos_align_center vc_separator-has-text"><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_l"><span style="border-color:#ed1b2f;" class="vc_sep_line"></span></span><h4>WHAT WE DO</h4><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_r"><span style="border-color:#ed1b2f;" class="vc_sep_line"></span></span></div><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 10px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1553613491183"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="text-align: center;">Custom clothing and PPE are important for most businesses. They reduce the risk of injury at work or simply protect from heat or cold. Furthermore, custom clothing is a great tool for building brand awareness while keeping employees safe and comfortable.</p><p style="text-align: center;">That is why we aim to be a world-class business generating long-term value while consistently providing high quality products at a competitive price. Even more, we provide a truly unique customer experience. Products are very easy to find and customise thanks to our customisation tool which is very modern and intuitive.</p><h4 style="text-align: center;">Choose from an impressive range of products to suit all of you PPE and workwear needs.</h4><p style="text-align: center;">Top quality services, fast turnaround times and competitive prices for custom clothing are achieved by using our state of the art printing and embroidery machines. Workwear is customised using the latest technology such as <a href="https://ppesuppliesdirect.com/customisation-techniques/">DTG, vinyl or screen printing as well as high volume embroidery.</a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Furthermore, our design and production teams will provide expert advice on clothing choice or customisation techniques. Moreover, we offer a wide range of services from creating bespoke graphics to digitising your artwork. Therefore, you can rely on us to get the job done right.</p><p style="text-align: center;">We launched as a small business in Kent, UK, focusing on delivering top quality personal protective equipment. We then quickly expanded to cover workwear and other safety solutions. Equally important, we improved every aspect of our business while employing more staff and moving in a larger premises.</p><h4 style="text-align: center;">We aim to be a one stop shop to meet all your needs.</h4></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></main></div></div></section><div class="megamenu-overlay"></div></div><footer id="apus-footer" class="apus-footer hidden-xs hidden-sm" role="contentinfo"><div class="footer-inner"><div class="footer-builder-wrapper full  footer-1"><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid main_footer"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-3"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_empty_space" style="height: 30px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_left  vc_custom_1552314335818"><figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure"><div class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey"><img width="190" height="71" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39;%20viewBox=&#39;0%200%20190%2071&#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-full" alt="" data-lazy-src="http://ppesuppliesdirect.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/PPE-Logo-190.png"><noscript><img width="190" height="71" src="http://ppesuppliesdirect.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/xPPE-Logo-190.png.pagespeed.ic.w8I9m6h_9g.webp" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-full" alt=""/></noscript></div></figure></div><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h5>Unit 12, Hill Park Farm<br> Wrotham Hill